data.meta_description: Provides a mailing address for requesting autographs and sending fan mail to Dolly Parton
data.text:
How to send your fan mail and autograph requests to Dolly Parton?:

If you want to request an autograph, follow the guidelines bellow. If you just want to mail a letter with the address above, and do not want anything back, then you can stop reading! If you live in USA send a properly stamped and self addressed envelope (minimum size 8.5" x 4") with your request letter and a photo. You can include a piece of cardboard to keep the photo from bending in shipping and also add "Do Not Bend" on the envelopes. Send your letter and wait. On average, there is going to be a 3+ month wait for a response. If you do not live in USA, you can purchase your american stamps here *For information on postage prices to receive a letter from USA click here.

Feedback received:

Music - Dolly Parton Success - June 18th, 2024

Sent 8x10 to address below on 5/6/24 and received it back signed on 6/17/24. c/o Dolly Parton Management 2401 12th Ave S. Nashville, TN 37204 Comment | View 6 comment(s) Dolly Parton- SUCCESS!!!! - June 17th, 2024

Sent Ms. Parton an 8x10, LOR and SASE on 2 FEB 24. Received my photo back signed in black on 15 JUN 24. Address used: Ms. Dolly Parton PO Box 150307 Nashville, TN 37215 http://surfmypictures.com/image/905375604141b8cb/qgce0.html http://surfmypictures.com/image/905375604141b8cb/ja94o.html Comment | View 1 comment(s) Dolly Parton Success - January 27th, 2024

I wrote to Dolly Parton on Jan. 5, 2024 and received a response on Jan 26, 2024. Very quick! Although I included a self-addressed stamped envelope, it was not used. The only thing in the envelope I received was a protected photo. I sent my original letter to PO Box 150307, Nashville, TN 37215 and the letter I received back had a return address of: Inca Hoots (A Dolly Parton Company) 2401 12th Ave S Nashville, TN 37204 http://surfmypictures.com/image/53460d9e7019b21f/ux27k.html Comment | View 3 comment(s)
